On 10/25/05 11:45 AM, "Greg Potts" <Greg(-at-)pottsfamily.ca> wrote:

> Hi Volks,
> 
> Does anyone know the pressure and volume specs for the fuel pump on a
> BN-2 heater?  I checked the archives but there's nothing specific.

10.7 - 12.7 cm3 in 2 minutes. The adjustment is done at screw in the end cap
of the regulator, turning to the right increases fuel.

This is from a 1969 VW fresh air heater manual.

